Then, apply the 'growth serum' to the resulting 0-value hybrid; this reliably creates a high-value 'grown' item (10-20). Be cautious with repeated 'growth serum' applications on already 'grown' items, as it can sometimes decrease value or have no further effect. The 'mutation catalyst' is extremely risky and almost always reduces value, so avoid using it.
